{"tid":1245724,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱去買豬嘴個事頭婆同講","createTime":"2019-06-20T12:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T01:58:49.000Z","uid":254923,"like":78,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"11620610ef58e7cbb7a0230c24016a896235d706","tid":1245724,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：事頭婆<br />\n<br />\n喺畀錢嗰陣事頭婆問我今日好多人買豬嘴喎你又買嚟做咩<br />\n<br />\n我都唔想講太多就求其答佢算鳩數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係咩 咁啱得咁橋掛 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：得啦後生仔 我明喎 聽日加油啦<br />\n<br />\n最後仲收返我成本價算，我先知道原來香港大人都有支持我地，令我對聽日更加充滿信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實上面都係我作出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我係真係有買豬嘴，但係個事頭婆淨係講我講今日多人買豬嘴喎，我只係講左係呀就無其他野 不過個故仔都係想所有聽日肯出嚟嘅香港人一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb82c378937590637b941a204405f9f45ea3d692","tid":1245724,"uid":204352,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:19:13.000Z","msg":"欺騙連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有心意分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日加油"},{"pid":"bcf3e27775a5212e3b4a04efde299b422f83327c","tid":1245724,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb82c378937590637b941a204405f9f45ea